# Directory structure for Docker Compose setup
# Create these directories OUTSIDE the SIRA code repository:
#
# Recommended structure (at same level as sira/ code directory):
#
# your_workspace/
# ├── sira/                    # SIRA code repository
# ├── sira_inputs/          # Your scenario data (outside repo)
# │   ├── scenario_1/
# │   │   ├── input/
# │   │   │   ├── config_*.json
# │   │   │   └── model_*.json
# │   │   └── output/          # SIRA writes outputs here
# │   └── scenario_2/
# └── sira_outputs/            # Additional consolidated outputs
